unittitle_ssm: Records of the Bureau of Public Occasions
abstract_ssm: The Records of the Bureau of Public Occasions contain a wide array of information related to the planning and hosting of University public events, commencement and commencement-related programs.  The records are arranged alphabetically in one series and consist mainly of administrative records, correspondence, drafts, notes, telegraphs, photographs, and photo contact sheets.
